51.3518, 50.7141, 48.9084, 48.6468, 49.1199, 49.3938, 48.5934, 48.8858, 48.9625, 48.7702, 48.6203, 48.2764, 48.4329, 48.4816, 49.9055, 49.0014, 48.0046, 46.9682, 47.06, 46.6978, 44.6059, 43.5339, 43.7623, 44.5559, 45.5713, 45.1942, 44.1855, 45.6066, 48.419, 49.9315, 49.6275, 48.9572, 48.1112, 47.7007, 48.5427, 49.8762, 49.9529, 49.8765, 50.2865, 50.8173, 51.3825, 50.5982, 50.7346, 50.8294, 51.322, 52.771, 51.9885, 53.7031, 52.9014, 52.3946, 52.7936, 53.2147, 54.5785, 54.6104, 55.5998, 55.6913, 54.7752, 55.587, 55.1474, 56.689, 55.5966, 55.6552, 55.0784, 55.1357, 54.5904, 54.1552, 54.356, 54.7889, 54.7371, 55.033, 57.1295, 56.3421, 55.1311, 59.3673, 56.1194, 54.6162, 54.2718, 55.1249, 55.4243, 55.0051, 54.4385, 54.3164, 56.1957, 55.0225, 56.1526, 56.0729, 55.2992, 55.9822, 57.4341, 56.6214, 57.4064, 57.958, 57.3414, 53.493, 53.053, 51.7663, 52.8582, 53.5118, 54.7322, 55.6066, 55.3792, 56.0894, 56.0479, 55.4994, 55.0762, 54.9092, 55.2109, 54.2639, 53.6735, 54.1277, 54.3246, 55.3085, 55.5188, 56.572, 56.9651, 56.442, 54.5108, 55.0361, 54.2264, 53.7852, 55.8346, 55.7872, 56.5886, 58.6077, 58.0206, 58.4485, 60.2309, 59.665, 59.881, 60.1935, 59.6646, 59.3432, 59.1562, 58.7032, 59.3313, 59.0397, 58.9895, 57.7248, 58.6131, 58.2357, 58.087, 58.0701, 59.5381, 60.8602, 59.2331, 58.8019, 57.8928, 61.5662, 60.8756, 62.4281, 64.714, 66.8585, 65.1512, 64.6744, 64.0291, 63.4115, 63.2979, 62.8056, 63.2812, 65.7682, 65.0737, 65.1122, 66.636, 66.9653, 67.4437, 67.2453, 67.4823, 67.4858, 67.82, 68.2781, 69.3045, 69.1597, 69.1293, 69.0862, 68.6366, 69.2377, 69.4333, 69.5294, 70.0426, 68.0808, 67.5125, 67.1216, 66.1623, 66.6578, 66.0408, 66.0843, 65.8232, 65.5418, 61.993, 62.6591, 63.4615, 62.5046, 60.851, 60.2084, 59.5449, 60.7697, 60.6626, 60.1314, 58.5823, 57.3502, 56.5256, 58.852, 58.8212, 59.9128, 59.1147, 58.5932, 58.7413, 60.9015, 60.2657, 60.4394, 58.3969, 57.8398, 59.1899, 58.664, 59.2475, 59.1865, 58.4117, 57.9385, 58.569, 59.3539, 58.7106, 56.8532, 54.7758, 54.2552, 54.2774, 54.8471, 55.1239, 53.9208, 54.5, 53.8397, 55.8406, 56.6054, 56.8147, 56.2991, 54.7232, 52.8433, 53.9546, 53.4066, 51.8164, 52.8411, 52.3062, 54.1158, 54.1264, 52.9241, 51.9603, 51.2107, 51.8559, 50.2889, 52.1279, 51.9831, 53.9107, 54.9828, 55.6894, 57.3538, 57.5114, 57.8779, 58.9577, 61.2898, 60.4939, 59.5206, 59.8146, 59.5612, 59.2109, 59.2537, 58.0882, 56.1185, 56.3965, 57.9046, 57.0459, 58.5122, 56.3527, 58.4867, 60.3625, 60.4379, 60.279, 59.0601, 58.637, 60.0132, 59.7203, 60.4802, 61.3213, 62.7276, 63.1742, 61.479, 62.5125, 63.0415, 63.6523, 64.2323, 63.2697, 61.314, 61.2335, 59.275, 57.5565, 56.6886, 57.8238, 56.8009, 57.0021, 57.025, 52.8096, 53.2857, 47.2577, 42.435, 44.9379, 46.8092, 46.1656], "summary_html": "<h1>反转因子的精细结构 -- 理想反转因子 M</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略将东吴证券提出的\"W式切割\"反转因子方法应用于商品期货。核心思路是：传统反转因子（如过去N日收益率）可以按日内交易活跃度进行\"切割\"——大单交易活跃日的涨跌幅具有更强的反转特性（信息驱动），而小单交易日的涨跌幅更接近噪声甚至呈现弱动量。通过分离这两部分并做差，得到\"理想反转因子\"M，其选股/选品种能力显著优于传统反转因子。</p>\n<p>在商品期货中，我们使用日频 amount/volume（平均成交金额/手数）作为\"平均单笔成交金额\"的代理指标。对每个品种回看过去N个交易日，按该指标排序分为高D组（大单日）和低D组（小单日），分别计算累积收益，M = M_high - M_low。高M品种（大单日涨幅大于小单日）倾向于反转——做空；低M品种倾向于继续——做多。等权组合N=20和N=40两个窗口，进一步降低参数敏感性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.23</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>0.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.0%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-18.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.08</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3430</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.83</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.47</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.69 / 0.95</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.34</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.36</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.7</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.44</span></td><td>1.1</td><td>0.5</td><td>0.03</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.45</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.59</span></td><td>1.91</td><td>0.33</td><td>1.59</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.92</span></td><td>0.55</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.1</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>open</code></td><td>开盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>high</code></td><td>最高价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>low</code></td><td>最低价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>amount</code></td><td>成交额</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>61</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3432</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>40.0</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>对品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">s</span>，回溯 <span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 个交易日，计算每日平均成交金额：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">D_t = \\frac{\\text{amount}_t}{\\text{volume}_t}</div>\n<p>将 <span class=\"math-tex\">N</span> 日按 <span class=\"math-tex\">D</span> 从大到小排序，取前 <span class=\"math-tex\">N/2</span> 为高D组，后 <span class=\"math-tex\">N/2</span> 为低D组：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">M_{\\text{high}} = \\prod_{t \\in \\text{highD}} (1 + R_t) - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">M_{\\text{low}} = \\prod_{t \\in \\text{lowD}} (1 + R_t) - 1</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">M = M_{\\text{high}} - M_{\\text{low}}</div>\n<p>截面排名后转连续信号 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\in [-1, 1]</span>，乘以波动率目标缩放系数得到仓位。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.74)</strong>: 初始实现了完整的W式切割逻辑，覆盖N=20/40/60三种窗口，每种搭配hold=5/10/20三种再平衡周期，加上M_high和M_low独立因子变体共12个。诊断发现N=20、hold=20是最优组合，短hold（5天）的变体Sharpe为负，说明信号衰减缓慢，频繁调仓反而增加了交易成本（换手率1.06）。截面IC仅0.006，时序IC=0.007（65%品种IC&gt;0），信号在部分品种有效。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.84)</strong>: 根据R1诊断，延长再平衡周期至hold=25并加入IC gate过滤弱品种。结果hold=25（M_N20_h25_raw Sharpe 0.84）确实优于hold=20（0.74），验证了信号慢衰减的判断。IC gate版本与非gate版本几乎相同（被dedup），说明品种过滤对该因子帮助有限。换手率降至0.85。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 1.00)</strong>: <strong>关键转折</strong>: 引入N=20与N=40的等权组合（M_combo_N20_N40），利用不同窗口的互补性降低波动（年化vol从66.5%降至46.8%），Sharpe从0.84提升至1.00。同时测试了更长hold（30, 40天）和VWAP替代指标，发现hold&gt;25开始退化（hold=30仅0.03），VWAP/close替代效果差（均为负），说明amount/volume是更好的大单活跃度指标。半样本Sharpe前1.31后1.09，策略在样本前后均稳健。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（daily），使用 amount 和 volume 计算平均成交金额</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（58个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 约25个交易日再平衡，属于中低频策略</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 原文使用A股逐笔\"成交笔数\"数据，期货端用 amount/volume 近似，可能有信息损失\n<p>- 截面IC较弱（0.010），主要靠时序IC（0.009）驱动收益 - 年度Sharpe波动较大（2019年-0.03，2022年-0.02），部分年份接近持平 - 最大回撤58%较高，建议结合其他因子分散风险</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>N_WINDOWS</code></td><td><code>[20, 40]</code></td><td>lookback windows for M factor</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>25</code></td><td>rebalance hold period</td></tr><tr><td><code>SPLIT_RATIO</code></td><td><code>0.5</code></td><td>top/bottom half split</td></tr><tr><td><code>MIN_VALID_RATIO</code></td><td><code>0.6</code></td><td>minimum valid data ratio in window</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9909</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 6.3s</li>\n</ul>"}